# Report

## EXISTING STRUCTURES

There are no existing structures to report.

## ERROR TIPS

### Inventory full errors during pickup
- The agent's inventory is full when attempting to pick up items. Ensure the inventory has sufficient space before attempting to pick up items. Consider dropping unnecessary items or crafting them into more compact forms.

### Could not extract errors
- The agent is failing to extract coal from an inserter, likely because the inserter is empty. Before attempting to extract, ensure that the target entity contains the item you want to extract.

### Could not insert errors
- The agent is failing to insert coal into an inserter because the inserter's inventory is full. Before attempting to insert, ensure that the target entity has space for the item you want to insert.

## NAMESPACE

There are no namespaces to report.
